jobInfo.postDescription:
Job Title: Junior Test engineer
Job Description:
We are looking for a motivated and detail-oriented Junior Tester to join our QA team. As a Junior Test engineer, you will be responsible for executing test cases, identifying bugs, and communicate with developer for the bug debugging. 
Key Responsibilities:
•	Execute manual test cases
•	Identify, report bugs and trouble shooting.
•	Collaborate with the development and QA teams to reproduce and resolve issues.
•	Assist in the creation and maintenance of test documentation
•	Perform regression testing to ensure existing functionality remains intact.
•	Contribute to continuous improvement of the testing process.
Required Skills and Qualifications:
•	Familiarity with software testing principles and methodologies.
•	Attention to detail and strong problem-solving skills.
•	Good communication skills. Good writing/reading skill in English.
•	Any Linux related knowledge is preferred
•	Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related field.
